t; id=&quot;volume-placement-80&quot; class=&quot;volume-video&quot; data-volume-player-choice=&quot;youtube&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;!- - ######## 视频尾声 ######## -->;&lt;div class=&quot;caption&quot;>;&lt;em>;The Vergecast 谈论 iPhone 16。&lt;/em>;&lt;/div>; &lt;/ div>; &lt;p id=&quot;ew1VHV&quot;>;除了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24232248/apple-event-september-iphone-16-date-time-live- Stream-watch-how-to-rumors&quot;>;新款 iPhone&lt;/a>;，苹果可能会宣布下一个主要软件更新的发布日期，包括 iOS 18、iPadOS 18、macOS 15 Sequoia...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24238537/apples-glowtime-iphone-16-event-how-to-watch-ios-18-apple-intelligence- ai&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24238537/apples-glowtime-iphone-16-event-how-to-watch-ios-18-apple-intelligence-ai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24238537/apples-glowtime-iphone-16-event-how-to-watch-ios-18-apple-intelligence-ai</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-07T16:00:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-07T16:00:03-04:00</updated><title> Nanoleaf历经八年终于推出智能开关</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xAFbqNxBTh7vRhfV7a9rDnJ-Sdw=/0x182:4000x2849/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73570677/Switch_Skylight_Hallway_4000x3000px.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Nanoleaf 的 Sense Plus 智能开关可无线控制 Nanoleaf 的灯光，包括其新的吸顶灯。&lt;/em>; |图片：Nanoleaf&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Ws9vqM&quot;>;经过近十年的发展，Nanoleaf的智能开关终于问世了。您可以预订 30 美元的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fnanoleaf.me%2Fen-US%2Fproducts%2Fessentials% 2Fsense-plus%2F%3Fcategory%3Dwireless-switch&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F7%2F24235620%2Fnanoleaf-sense-plus-smart-switch- thread-matter-litewave&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Sense Plus 智能无线“随处”开关&lt;/a>;今天推出，预计 10 月份发货。但要达到这一点，Nanoleaf 必须放弃采用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23165855/thread-smart-home-protocol-matter-apple-google-interview&quot;>;Thread &lt;/a>; 并创建一个名为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fnanoleaf.me%2Fen-US 的新专有协议%2Fproducts%2Fessentials%2Fsense-plus%2F%3Fcategory%3Dwireless-switch%23%3A%7E%3Atext%3DWhat%2520is%2520Nanoleaf%2520Litewave%253F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww .theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F7%2F24235620%2Fnanoleaf-sense-plus-smart-switch-thread-matter-litewave&quot; rel=&quot;Recommended nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Litewave&lt;/a>;。&lt;/a>;。 p>; &lt;p id=&quot;EufDIV&quot;>;电池供电的设备为 Nanoleaf 的智能照明系统带来物理控制，让您按下按钮即可打开或关闭灯光、调暗或调亮或改变颜色。此外，内置运动和光线传感器可让 Sense 根据房间条件调整照明。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;eX6v5z&quot;>;&lt; q>;“我们需要确保我们的产品能够可靠地工作，同时减少对平台的依赖。”Gimmy Chu&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;An9y38&quot;>;The Sense，一个版本这是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/1/3/21047870/nanoleaf-learning-series-smart-lighting-hexagons&quot;>;f...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24235620/nanoleaf-sense-plus-smart-switch-thread-matter-litewave&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24235620/nanoleaf-sense-plus-smart-switch-thread-matter-litewave" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24235620/nanoleaf-sense-plus-smart-switch-thread-matter-litewave</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-07T15:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-07T15:00:00-04:00</updated><title> TIFF 2024：来自多伦多的所有最新电影评论</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2024 年多伦多国际电影节将于 2024 年 9 月 3 日在安大略省多伦多举行，TIF